{"tid":1656381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽講隸屬港島總區衝鋒隊警署警長的林志偉每日有四個gay4貼心保護","createTime":"2019-10-15T14:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T14:53:54.000Z","uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"773776f9e6539e137431af05acc79c7f183bfbb4","tid":1656381,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:30:37.000Z","msg":"原理係搵支太陽能電筒照住另一支太樣能電筒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隸屬港島總區衝鋒隊警署警長的林志偉原為協會第一副主席，今屆當選主席，任期6年，他致辭指出，近年有人以「違法達義」的口號鼓動青年人破壞法紀，「我為這班被蒙蔽而失去光明前途的年輕人感到婉惜」。他又表示警察肩負執法職責，代表本港的法治，不能被挑釁，因此將會以協會名義，向立法會爭取就辱警罪或侮辱公職人員罪立法，以保障警察尊嚴。他並指出，警察是國家的人民，有愛國權利，不認同不應有愛國立場，「警員一定要愛國，而愛國最好的表現就是做好警隊的工作」。"},{"pid":"429da7a5c19261083fbc800494b67a3b54dc6fd5","tid":1656381,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2fbaa216e0a2cbf200ec71e37c1e3793504b5208","tid":1656381,"uid":5822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"警署警長咪又係頂薪3皮幾 佢係咁狗吠做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cf5d7ad65c5e2644b660e1e823914650870325","tid":1656381,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"因為佢好重要架，肩負起替其他忍屎忍屎既警察上京食龍蝦叫雞既重任"},{"pid":"b0636484b0dea8ea03ffb62ec9410c8ca97ef4c6","tid":1656381,"uid":23041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:37:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">警察是國家的人民</span><br />\n香港人唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1f3851ceff9a573e294a4e738086412093507b","tid":1656381,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fbaa216e0a2cbf200ec71e37c1e3793504b5208","tid":1656381,"uid":5822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20